title: X-23 (X23) v2 001 (2010|C2C|One-Shot|Minutemen-Rocn King)
description: After seeing that the recent upload I posted was officially considered X23 v3 by Marvel, I tried to figure out what exactly was v2. Well, it is apparently only this lone Women of Marvel One-Shot. What? Seriously, this is the whole "Volume 2" of X-23! Anyway, regardless of that moronic numbering, this is still worth reading as it is written by the excellent Marjorie Liu - who also handled her ongoing series and tied into it - and features some great art by Felipe Andrade and Nuno Alves. Thanks to Minutemen for the scan, please seed and enjoy! :-)
